      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Repeals the 6/30/27 deadline by which the Maui State Veterans Home must be assimilated into a state agency having a Maui affiliation.  Requires the transfer of the Maui State Veterans Home to be completed as soon as practicable.  (SD1)"
    }
